<p class="v2-structure-link"><b>Message Structure:</b> <a href="StructureDefinition-PEX_P07.html">PEX_P07</a></p>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The primary application of the PEX message is to transfer information related to an adverse event occurring while a patient was exposed to a product. The P08 event is an unsolicited update of an individual product experience report.</p>
